 屌你個系"},{"pid":"584d154f38b28606d7056fb0b47b5d965cf2af25","tid":778312,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9599fc70466975bce55f12a9e669db443969056a","tid":778312,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"點會識變壓啊 屌你個系"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"我果個係新款多用途旅行插，個插有usb,type c,個頭又內置fuse。買果時叫國際旅行用變壓器，咁咪以為佢有電子變壓囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實咪又係一個多用途旅行插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba4109918731724aec99ccd8bb538fc42197553","tid":778312,"uid":127466,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"醒到咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  知道電壓有分別, 又唔識買個變壓器, 唔燒屋算好彩. <br />\n如果個風筒有 2000W, 變壓器仲大過個風筒, 要買 2500W 先夠用.  鴨記下揾無人幫你整, 不過 total loss 機會都幾大. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn10.dcfever.com/media/trade/18/5/5/23/624942_1525533190_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn10.dcfever.com%2Fmedia%2Ftrade%2F18%2F5%2F5%2F23%2F624942_1525533190_1.jpg&h=c1fe2943&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55b6b05c06bf83ce1b5b3744c58d993d3bc93189","tid":778312,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"無眼睇你...當垃圾掉左佢啦"}]}